CURRENT
FF events size
BP+SI+CX at Bossbot (scheduler)
CX = amount events bytes in buffer
SI = current position = offset of BP, 2 byte
LOOP for processing
/dev/kbd handler

PLAN
text reader for saving current point

DREAM
interrupt processing without CLI/STI: change interrupt vector
comment from external file
view lower shift

DONE
mask for border buffers
